mistral.reason: "Miracle" by Cascada was written by Yann Peifer and Manuel Reuter, not DJ Manian. While DJ Manian (Manuel Reuter) produced the track under his production name DJ Manian, he did not write it.

gemma2.reason: Multiple pieces of text state the song "Miracle" was written by Yann Peifer and Manuel Reuter, who use the production names Yanou and DJ Manian.

llama3.1.reason: According to information provided, the song "Miracle" by Cascada was written by Yann Peifer and Manuel Reuter, who also produced the track under their production names Yanou and DJ Manian, and then later a song called 'Miracle' by TOMORROW X TOGETHER was released in 2024 which makes it impossible for DJ Manian to be the writer of both songs.
